        <![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.designboom.com/project/fibonacci-shelf/">The Fibonacci Shelf</a> by designer Peng Wang might not be the most functional piece of furniture, but I still want one. </p>

<p><img src="http://also.kottke.org/misc/images/fibonacci-shelf-01.jpg" width="640" height="752" border="0" alt="Fibonacci Shelf" /></p>

