        <![CDATA[<p>No hunger. No pollution. No disease. Wired's Amy Maxmen welcomes you to the age of copy and paste DNA editing <a href="http://www.wired.com/2015/07/crispr-dna-editing-2/">and the end of life as we know it</a>.</p>

